phase2.explanation:
🤖 **Common Room mistakes and fixes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| No primary key | Add @PrimaryKey |
| Nullable primitive | Use non-nullable |
| No default values | Add default values |
| Blocking operation | Use suspend |
| Nullable return | Use non-nullable |
| No Flow | Use Flow for observing |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
// 1. Add primary key
@PrimaryKey(autoGenerate = true)
val id: Int = 0

// 2. Use non-nullable
val health: Int

// 3. Add default values
val level: Int = 1

// 4. Use suspend
@Insert
suspend fun insertPlayer(player: PlayerEntity)

// 5. Use non-nullable
suspend fun getPlayers(): List<PlayerEntity>

// 6. Use Flow for observing
fun getPlayers(): Flow<List<PlayerEntity>>

// 7. Handle errors
viewModelScope.launch {
    try { /* insert */ } catch (e: Exception) { /* handle */ }
}
```

